{"tid":874631,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【港珠澳大橋】截至下午3時有868架次車輛使用","createTime":"2018-10-24T10:37:31.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-24T11:30:19.000Z","uid":102732,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"2c0abcad5af016aebe4c36a74d80a89a2bcbeff2","tid":874631,"uid":102732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-24T10:37:31.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E6%B8%AF%E7%8F%A0%E6%BE%B3%E5%A4%A7%E6%A9%8B-%E6%88%AA%E8%87%B3%E4%B8%8B%E5%8D%883%E6%99%82%E6%9C%89868%E6%9E%B6%E6%AC%A1%E8%BB%8A%E8%BC%9B%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8-095700987.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E7%258F%25A0%25E6%25BE%25B3%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E6%25A9%258B-%25E6%2588%25AA%25E8%2587%25B3%25E4%25B8%258B%25E5%258D%25883%25E6%2599%2582%25E6%259C%2589868%25E6%259E%25B6%25E6%25AC%25A1%25E8%25BB%258A%25E8%25BC%259B%25E4%25BD%25BF%25E7%2594%25A8-095700987.html&d=oV03Jz3tVDaVEDGqvmAcKC7bS0i5kAixZS1hjGmvpwM%3D&h=22f99303\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E6%B8%AF%E7%8F%A0%E6%BE%B3%E5%A4%A7%E6%A9%8B-%E6%88%AA%E8%87%B3%E4%B8%8B%E5%8D%883%E6%99%82%E6%9C%89868%E6%9E%B6%E6%AC%A1%E8%BB%8A%E8%BC%9B%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8-095700987.html</a><br />\n<br />\n【星島日報報道】港珠澳大橋通車首日，大橋管理局公布，截至下午3時，共有868架次車輛使用大橋往來三地，當中往香港方向行駛的車輛有297架次，往珠澳方向的就有571架次。<br />\n<br />\n使用大橋往來的車輛當中最多的是小型客車，有446架次，其次是過境巴士和穿梭小巴有401架次，貨車則有21架次。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n多人用到<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  一半係巴士"},{"pid":"125f9750ded6d4b877d612ce3257058f78d92a84","tid":874631,"uid":108347,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-24T10:38:33.000Z","msg":"預計幾多話?大聲啲?聽唔到?"},{"pid":"9b60276f8c4fe1a031106058c415ce5dfcbcc3c4","tid":874631,"uid":38528,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"quote":{"pid":"125f9750ded6d4b877d612ce3257058f78d92a84","tid":874631,"uid":108347,"lik